                                    <a class="sf-category" href="https://catholicherald.co.uk/section/commentandblogs/" rel="category tag">Comment</a>                                    <a class="sf-category" href="https://catholicherald.co.uk/section/comment-and-feature/" rel="category tag">Opinion &amp; Features</a>                            </div>

        
        <h3 class="sf-card__title" itemprop="name headline">
            <a class="sf-card__title-link" href="https://catholicherald.co.uk/magazine/beauty-can-lead-to-faith-an-interview-with-the-director-of-the-vatican-museums/" itemprop="url">&lsquo;Beauty can lead to faith&rsquo; &ndash; an interview with the director of the Vatican Museums</a>        </h3>
        <div class="sf-card__excerpt" itemprop="description">
            <p>Barbara Jatta, the first female director of the Vatican Museums, is determined they should contain more than just ‘musty memories’</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sf-card__meta">
        <div class="sf-author" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
            <a class="sf-author__link" href="https://catholicherald.co.uk/author/desmond-o-grady/" rel="author" itemprop="url"><span itemprop="name">Desmond O&#039;Grady</span></a>                        <meta itemprop="worksFor" content="Catholic Herald">
